</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername direction="in">argv</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Array of arguments as set in the plugin JSON configuration file trough the arguments field (&quot;ExtraRPCPlugins/i/arguments&quot; or &quot;/RSCServer/RPCPlugins/i/arguments&quot;).</para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para>If this function returns false, the plugin is not initialized and pind will not use it </para>
