    <briefdescription>
<para>Holds function pointers to basic common pind plugin functionality. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This structure should not be allocated directly. It should be filled and returned as part of <ref refid="structIRPCPlugin" kindref="compound">IRPCPlugin</ref>.</para>
<para>This is also the first member of <ref refid="structIRPCPlugin" kindref="compound">IRPCPlugin</ref>. So casting an <ref refid="structIRPCPlugin" kindref="compound">IRPCPlugin</ref> to <ref refid="structIPindPlugin" kindref="compound">IPindPlugin</ref> should work, providing a C style &quot;object oriented&quot; way of implementing plugins. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
